StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [sp_ImportNewQsns]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
As
SET NOCOUNT ON SET ANSI_WARNINGS OFF
INSERT INTO QSN(QSN_ID, MOS, RUC, ASSIGNED_ORG_ID, GENDER, SPLIT_INCREMENT, QSN_PIVOT_DATE, COMPONENT_CODE, MSC, MCC_CODE, RECRUITING_ORGANIZATION_ID, STATUS, FY, USER_LOGIN, UPDATE_DATE )
SELECT QSN, IMOS, RESRUC, ASSIGNED_ORG_ID, SEX, IIADT, PIVDATE, COMPCODE, CONVERT(CHAR(1),MSC_CODE) AS MSC, MCC_CODE, RECRUITING_ORGANIZATION_ID, 'A' AS STATUS, FISCAL_YEAR, 'SA' AS USER_LOGIN, GetDate() AS UPDATE_DATE FROM READY_TO_IMPORT_QSN WHERE IMPORTED IS NULL
UPDATE READY_TO_IMPORT_QSN SET IMPORTED = 1
SET NOCOUNT OFF SET ANSI_WARNINGS ON
